Get ready for a world of hilarious monster mischief and alien antics in this

residents of Area 50-Something embark on fun-filled adventures
under the not-too-watchful eye of General Monger.

Vornicarn: A new alien, Sta'abi, comes to Earth in search of a ferocious beast
called Vornicarn. Soon, everyone is on a chase in order to save the planet from
Vornicarn's terror! However, much to our friends of Area Fifty-Something's
surprise, Sta'abi has her own plans for the alien pet.
